description:
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting new position to support the current Fire Officer at Calderdale and Huddersfield NHS Foundation Trust. The successful candidate will assist the current Fire Officer in the practical application of fire safety. This role will include undertaking Fire Risk Assessments, delivery of fire training and the development of management control plans. In order to fulfil the requirements of the job the post holder will be expected to undertake a structured fire safety training and education programme appropriate to the role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameKeith RawnsleyJob titleFire OfficerEmail addresskeith.rawnsley@cht.nhs.ukTelephone number07867550332&lt;/p&gt;
